            "reviews": "“An innovative adventure of an angered Square button unleashed from its controller’s gamepad.”<br>4/5 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://indiegamereviewer.com/review-bad-pad-early-access/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Indie Game Reviewer</a><br><br>“Composed entirely in-house, there is a deliciously crunchy power metal score for each room that seamlessly transitions as you make your way through the game. Cutscenes are done as full musical numbers, giving the whole thing a Tenacious D feel.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://ready-up.net/2018/08/03/game-review-game-review-telling-game-devs-what-to-do-bad-pad-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Ready Up</a><br><br>“Must Buy! We don't always have time to review everything, but we've personally played Bad Pad and think it's worth a buy. A great 2D platformer with an awesome soundtrack!”<br><a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/curators/curatorsrecommending/?appid=517210\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Steam Curators</a><br>",
